All garments are crafted with care using premium natural fabrics.

Washing Instructions:
- Hand wash in cold water with gentle detergent.
- Do not bleach.
- Lay flat to dry; avoid direct sunlight.
- Iron low if needed on reverse side.

Tip: Store in a breathable cloth bag when not in use to prevent fabric stress and preserve shape.

